Oh god..

this is what i've done to (hopefully) make this scanner work on OSX.

/System/Library/Extensions/FTDIUSBSerialDriver.kext/Contents/Info.plist

copy the one in this directory over there after you install the driver from 
http://www.ftdichip.com/Drivers/VCP/MacOSX/FTDIUSBSerialDriver_v2_2_16.dmg

(see the Tech Note TN_105 at http://www.ftdichip.com/Support/Documents/TechnicalNotes/TN_105%20Adding%20Support%20for%20New%20FTDI%20Devices%20to%20Mac%20Driver.pdf)

The device information is:
